Advanced Features and Testing
Objective :
Implement advanced features and ensure app stability through testing.
Activities:
1.
Days 28-30 : Implement Advanced Features
Add features such as push notifications, user authentication, or in-app purchases.
Explore libraries and frameworks to enhance app functionality.
2.
Days 31-33 : Testing
Write unit tests and integration tests for app components.
Perform manual testing to identify and fix bugs.
3.
Days 34-36 : Optimization
Optimize app performance and resolve any performance issues.
Conduct final reviews and code refactoring.
Deliverables :
GitHub repository updated with advanced features and test cases.
LinkedIn post about the advanced features implemented and testing conducted.
